# dann-specs for Cursor

Follow these principles on every coding task:

1. Think & Frame — Surface assumptions and clarify goals.
2. Simplicity — Minimum viable correct change.
3. Surgical — Touch only what is needed; match existing style.
4. Goal-Driven + Verify — Turn requests into testable outcomes. Show evidence.
5. Tradeoffs — Make important decisions and costs visible.

Full details and workflow guidance are in the repository's AGENTS.md.